      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and blood damage model selection justified against VAD-relevant flow physics; sensitivity to model form alternatives quantified.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected with limited justification for rotating-frame hemolysis flows. Power-law blood damage model used; no sensitivity study against Giersiepen-Wurzinger or Faghih-Sharp alternatives. Cross-study synthesis evidence (multi-study-synthesis node) indicates systematic underprediction in gap regions. Achieved Gradation 2."
